{
  "stem": "24958.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From-- there was an article-- a one page-- regards from prisoners-- not from prisoners-- it was from ex-prisoners from Dachau to their families in Poland.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, between all those, there were, Henry Rosner and his son.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So this is how I find out that he is alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had to go, but I didn't know how to-- how to communicate!",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no telephone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no mail.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no way of communicating.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to my girlfriend, [NON-ENGLISH], you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm gonna go on the way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm gonna try to go to Dachau and see what's happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she said-- she said to me, I go with you. she had-- she her husband, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we-- we got on the way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got-- took us about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were no trains, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Partly there were trains, partly there were no trains, partly we are-- we are-- we schmoozed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We talked with some English soldiers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They take us somewheres.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we got-- we found some Americans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got to Munchen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Munchen-- and there we found-- I found my husband-- my husband and my son.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, this-- this I cannot tell you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is-- this is something which is undescribable-- undescribable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have no words to tell you that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was in September-- September 1945.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my husband-- while he was in Dachau, on the end, when the American army came in, he befriended with one [NON-ENGLISH], major, Dr.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Morse.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a dentist by profession.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was an amateur cello player.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he wanted to play.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was another prisoner, a Polish guy-- [NON-ENGLISH] was his name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a piano player.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my husband was the violinist.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
